## Fase 3: Bug Fixes Pós-QA

**Data:** 2026-04-26
**Task ID:** qa-fix-1

### Bugs Found and Fixed

1. **AnimatedCounter starting at 0** → Changed to start at target value, animate on reveal
2. **`&amp;` rendered literally in hero eyebrow** → Fixed to plain `&`
