## Task ID: 4-b - UI Enhancement: WhatsApp Float + Scroll Progress
### Work Task
Create two new floating UI components (WhatsApp button + scroll progress bar) and integrate them into the page.

### Work Summary
- **WhatsAppFloat** (`src/components/advologos/whatsapp-float.tsx`): Floating green button fixed at bottom-left with pulse animation, tooltip on hover, appears after 800px scroll, opens WHATSAPP_URL in new tab. Uses `group` + `group-hover:opacity-100` for tooltip visibility.
- **ScrollProgress** (`src/components/advologos/scroll-progress.tsx`): Thin 3px progress bar fixed at top of viewport (z-[200]) with crimson gradient, uses `scaleX` transform for GPU performance, 0.1s linear transition.
- **globals.css**: Added `@keyframes whatsapp-pulse` animation section.
- **page.tsx**: Imported and placed both components — ScrollProgress before Navbar, WhatsAppFloat after BackToTop.
- ESLint: 0 errors, 0 warnings. Dev server: 200 OK.

