## Task ID: 4-a - FAQ Section Component
### Work Task
Create a new FAQ section component with shadcn Accordion, double bezel styling, and staggered ScrollReveal animations.

### Work Summary
- **faq-section.tsx** (`src/components/advologos/faq-section.tsx`): New client component with:
  - `id="faq"` and `aria-label="Perguntas frequentes"` for accessibility
  - Section label "05 — Perguntas Frequentes" with crimson line prefix (matches other sections)
  - Heading "Dúvidas comuns. / Respostas diretas." using serif font
  - Intro paragraph explaining Advologos approach
  - 6 FAQ items using shadcn `Accordion` in single-collapsible mode
  - "Double bezel" pattern: outer border + inner rounded card per item
  - AccordionTrigger styled with `text-[var(--editorial)] font-semibold text-[14px]` and crimson hover
  - AccordionContent styled with `text-[var(--prata)] text-[13px] leading-[1.65]`
  - Each item wrapped in `ScrollReveal` with incremental delay (1–6)
- **constants.ts**: Added `FAQ_ITEMS` export with 6 Q&A pairs in Portuguese covering firm size, OAB compliance, timelines, social media, package migration, and revision process
- **globals.css**: Added `[data-reveal][data-delay="6"]` with 480ms delay for 6th FAQ item
- **page.tsx**: Imported `FAQSection` and placed it between `AuthoritySection` and `CTASection`
- ESLint: 0 errors, 0 warnings. Dev server: 200 OK.

