## Task ID: 5-c - Stats Ribbon, Reusable Logo, Mobile Polish
### Work Task
Three deliverables: (A) horizontal stats ribbon section between Hero and Problem, (B) reusable AdvologosLogo component replacing inline logo text, (C) mobile responsive polish across 5 components.

### Work Summary

**Task A — Stats Ribbon:**
- Created `src/components/advologos/stats-ribbon.tsx` — new client component with 4 animated stat counters (150+ Marcas entregues, 98% Taxa de aprovação, 3 anos De operação, 12x Média de retorno)
- Uses IntersectionObserver-based `AnimatedStat` sub-component with cubic ease-out animation
- Wrapped in `ScrollReveal` for entrance animation; 2-col mobile / 4-col desktop grid layout
- Integrated into `page.tsx` between `<Hero />` and `<ProblemSection />`

**Task B — Reusable Logo:**
- Created `src/components/advologos/advologos-logo.tsx` — server component accepting `className` prop
- Renders "Advo" in editorial color + "logos" in crimson, using serif font
- Replaced inline logo text in `navbar.tsx` (desktop link + Sheet title) and `footer.tsx` (logo column)
- All 3 instances now use `<AdvologosLogo />` with appropriate size class

**Task C — Mobile Responsive Polish:**
1. `hero.tsx` — Reduced mobile top/bottom padding: `pt-40 pb-32` → `pt-32 pb-20`
2. `services-section.tsx` — Increased mobile card gap: `gap-4` → `gap-5`
3. `method-section.tsx` — Responsive step card padding: `p-[22px] px-6` → `px-4 py-4 md:px-6 md:py-[22px]`
4. `authority-section.tsx` — Responsive OAB notice padding: `px-5 py-4` → `px-4 py-3 md:px-5 md:py-4`
5. `cta-section.tsx` — Responsive CTA inner padding: `py-[72px]` → `py-12 md:py-[72px]`

**Verification:** ESLint 0 errors, 0 warnings. Dev server compiling successfully with 200 OK.

