## Task ID: 5-a - Testimonial Carousel + FAQ Navigation
### Work Task
Replace static testimonials with an auto-rotating carousel (framer-motion) in the Authority section, and add FAQ link to navigation (navbar + footer).

### Work Summary
- **authority-section.tsx**: Complete rewrite of the testimonials area — replaced 3 stacked testimonial cards with a single `TestimonialCarousel` component featuring:
  - Auto-play every 6 seconds with pause on hover (`useState` for `isPaused`)
  - framer-motion `AnimatePresence` + `motion.div` for smooth crossfade/slide transitions (opacity + y-axis, 0.4s duration with custom easing)
  - Dot indicators below the active testimonial (3 dots: crimson 24px pill when active, 6px gray circle otherwise)
  - Avatar circle with author initials (first letter of first name + first letter of last name, crimson bg with border)
  - Quote marks preserved (`.quote-mark` decorative element)
  - Double-bezel card styling preserved (outer border + inner rounded with `p-1.25`)
  - `overflow-hidden` on outer container for clean animation clipping
  - `min-h-[220px]` to prevent layout shift during transitions
  - OAB Notice card remains below the carousel in the same right column
- **constants.ts**: Added `{ href: '#faq', label: 'FAQ' }` to `NAV_LINKS` array. Removed `as const` assertion to avoid type narrowing issues with the expanded array. This automatically propagates FAQ to both desktop and mobile navbar (navbar already iterates NAV_LINKS).
- **footer.tsx**: Added FAQ link (`#faq`, label "Perguntas frequentes") after the Contato link in the navigation column.
- ESLint: 0 errors, 0 warnings. Dev server: all compilations successful with 200 OK responses.

