**Task A — FAQ Search/Filter (faq-section.tsx):**
- Added `useState` for `query` search state and `useMemo` for filtered items (case-insensitive match on question OR answer)
- Added Search input with `Search` icon (lucide-react) absolutely positioned inside input, styled per spec
- Added counter text "Exibindo {count} de {total} perguntas" below input
- Moved FAQ description paragraph to `delay={3}` (was delay=2), search input wrapped in `delay={2}`
- Non-matching items hidden with smooth animation: opacity + max-height transition (500ms, ease-expo)
