- Each card displays a unique 48px lucide-react icon (`text-[var(--crimson)] opacity-10`)

**Task D — Enhanced Footer Social Links (constants.ts + footer.tsx):**
- Added `SOCIAL_LINKS` export to `constants.ts` with icon name, href, label, and follower count (12.5K, 8.2K, 3.1K)
