- Follower text styled: `text-[9px] text-[var(--nevoa)] tracking-wide`

**CSS (globals.css):**
- Added `.faq-item-wrap` with transition on opacity, max-height, margin-bottom, padding (500ms, ease-expo)
- Added `.faq-item-hidden` for hidden state (max-height: 0, opacity: 0, pointer-events: none)
- Added `.faq-empty-state` with `@keyframes faq-fade-in` for empty results message animation

